{
  "stem": "5740.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as he-- he, he couldn't read it because it was in English.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said, I'm going to give it to the authorities and [SPEAKING GERMAN], which means it will cost the head, one of yours.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said to [NON-ENGLISH]-- [NON-ENGLISH] was-- had a sister in the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I said to [NON-ENGLISH], [NON-ENGLISH] if anybody goes, I go, because you have a sister.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that story she told my daughter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What, in fact, happened?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to the [NON-ENGLISH], and I said, look, I have in the next village here, which is also a concentration camp, I have a sister there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she wrote me that letter in Polish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he, he gave it back to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he didn't take the matter--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, he didn't-- [SIGHS] And I tell you what, that I still consider myself pretty lucky.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Being in the camps for three years and three months, I survived pretty good.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was lucky.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't get any of the-- at the end, the last days of the war, which I didn't know that they are the last days of the war, I felt that I am getting sick.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I couldn't even eat what they gave me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you know, you have such a specific tongue when we are getting paratyphoid.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had, I had the tongue already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It, it has got a circle of red around it, a round circle.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's one of the signs--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A sign of the paratyphoid.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But up until that very end time, you actually remained--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Relatively well.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was a strong one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we were, when we were working outside and we were digging the trenches for the--",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
